{"tid":757103,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖有透)話説最近我睇左套輕小説..女主係公廁..都算係重NTR","createTime":"2018-07-26T14:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T19:45:57.000Z","uid":6327,"like":13,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"de29e5a0fe27c83c60d8201c60a0311de07243fe","tid":757103,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T14:01:59.000Z","msg":"套野叫做  <span style=\"color: red;\">旅團粉碎機的那女孩如果被我已讀無視了會露出什麽表情呢</span><br />\n我只睇左第一卷<br />\n講男主原本個team人集合左各個職業既戰鬥精英 <br />\n途中執到女主角  女主角失左憶<br />\n一開始以為組隊戰鬥類輕小説 <br />\n然後睇個女主點樣誘惑男主 <br />\n女主原來係聖母類型 姐係人人愛我 我愛人人<br />\n但睇落去會發現女主原來有用同樣方式對待男主d隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到尾段開始嘈大鑊 原來除左男主幾乎所有人已經同女主上過床<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw我睇完第一卷覺得麻麻地  晤推薦大家曬時間去睇<br />\n請問大家有冇d ntr類可以介紹me睇下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/215222_dea19a1fee12ae59b037cfe8680216ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F215222_dea19a1fee12ae59b037cfe8680216ee.jpg&h=8be0c4b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/220114_e1a3159a4439429fc055d250ae4c311b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F220114_e1a3159a4439429fc055d250ae4c311b.jpg&h=6351aac5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01ac2e7f6c9d3109321f76e3149473d6b279e440","tid":757103,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T14:21:38.000Z","msg":"有冇睇宅男社團的公主殺人事件<br />\n不過漫畫嚟"},{"pid":"3b25e8273b275c16a05c868e329b925153a75849","tid":757103,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01ac2e7f6c9d3109321f76e3149473d6b279e440","tid":757103,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T14:21:38.000Z","msg":"有冇睇宅男社團的公主殺人事件<br />\n不過漫畫嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T14:24:11.000Z","msg":"聽個名都似係d毒撚圍女嘈大鑊